---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
        title="About - Combda"
        description="Learn about Combda's mission, values, and team. Discover how we deliver expert IT infrastructure and technology solutions."
>
    <Navbar/>
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-teal-100">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">About Combda</h1>

                <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                        Combda is a premier IT services company dedicated to transforming businesses through
                        innovative technology solutions. We specialize in providing comprehensive IT infrastructure,
                        cloud migration, cybersecurity, and DevOps consulting services.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                        To empower businesses with reliable, scalable, and secure technology solutions that
                        drive growth and operational excellence. We believe in building long-term partnerships
                        with our clients, ensuring their technology infrastructure evolves with their business needs.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
                    <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
                        <li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We deliver high-quality solutions that exceed expectations</li>
                        <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We stay ahead of technology trends to provide cutting-edge
                            solutions
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Our clients can count on us for consistent, dependable service
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Partnership:</strong> We work collaboratively with our clients as trusted advisors
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Why Choose Combda?</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                        With years of experience in the IT industry, our team brings deep expertise and a
                        proven track record of successful implementations. We understand that every business
                        is unique, which is why we tailor our solutions to meet your specific requirements
                        and budget constraints.
                    </p>

                    <div class="bg-teal-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-teal-200">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-2">Ready to Transform Your IT
                            Infrastructure?</h3>
                        <p class="text-teal-700 mb-4">
                            Let's discuss how Combda can help your business leverage technology for growth and success.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#contact"
                           class="bg-teal-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-teal-700 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out inline-block">
                            Get in Touch
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <Footer/>
</BaseLayout>